txt.en: You have destroyed the collection of enemy weapons, limiting the number that can be used against you and your allies while traversing Mordor.
Find a suitable place to dispose of the weapons
You should find a suitable place to dispose of the weapons

By defeating nefarious enemies, you will gain their discarded weapons and prevent others from making use of these brutal instruments of war. Who knows how many more blades lay scattered throughout Talath Úrui?
You hurl the weapons in the lava lake where they quickly melt
Dâr Mauzur is sparsely populated with many who served under Ugrukhôr before the fall of Sauron.
Weapons can be found at Dâr Mauzur.\n\nYou should collect any enemy weapons that you find in Dâr Mauzur.
